  <brief_title>Comparison of Soft Toothbrush and Brushless Cleaner in Their Ability to Remove Plaque From Teeth</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Soft Toothbrush and Brushless Cleaner in Their Ability to Remove Plaque From Teeth</official_title>
  <sponsors>
